parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the engine management system can cause the engine to malfunction, leading to reduced performance, decreased fuel efficiency, and potentially causing damage to other engine components.
symptoms: Check engine light and DTC light on the dashboard

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the "engine management" fuse can cause electrical systems to malfunction, leading to a range of issues including engine problems, electrical fires, and potentially causing damage to other components.
